Name Rascal/Libraries/Prelude/Set/getOneFrom
Synopsis Pick a random element from a set.
Function &T getOneFrom(set[&T] st) throws EmptySet
Usage import Set;
Description Also see takeOneFrom.
Examples 
rascal>import Set;
ok
rascal>getOneFrom({1,2,3,4});
int: 2
rascal>getOneFrom({1,2,3,4});
int: 1
rascal>getOneFrom({1,2,3,4});
int: 3
rascal>getOneFrom({1,2,3,4});
int: 1
